item.title: CVE-2019-10249|2024-08-04T22:17:19.691Z -- the%20eclipse%20foundation -- eclipse%20xtext
item.description: All Xtext & Xtend versions prior to 2.18.0 were built using HTTP instead of HTTPS file transfer and thus the built artifacts may have been compromised.
